t changes to the overall concept.&#10;4. The Welsh government is also considering creating a directory of resources to implement the Welsh dimension in the new curriculum, as recommended by the Learned Society of Wales. This proposal will be part of the ongoing work to identify necessary resources to support the curriculum.">
