necessary.&#10;5. External evaluation by Estyn: The Welsh government has established that Estyn, the education inspectorate for Wales, will assess schools' ability to deliver self-evaluations effectively. This external evaluation will ensure a consistent standard of self-evaluation across schools in Wales and promote continuous improvement.">
