engaging work environment for educators from various curriculum backgrounds.&#10;&#10;5. Addressing pedagogical differences: Acknowledging that there may be pedagogical concepts unfamiliar to teachers from different systems, ongoing professional learning can help bridge these gaps and ensure that all educators are equipped to provide high-quality instruction in the Welsh classroom.">
