that you've received during the feedback period on the draft curriculum.&#10;Speaker: Kirsty Williams AM&#10;Content: Thank you, Chair. If I may, I think it's important to understand what the level of that feedback has been. So, there was a concerted effort and a plan drawn up to try and ensure that there was as">
